###

### Add given point to the nearest edge in the square
PUT http://localhost:8000/square/16/add_point
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "point": {
    "type": "Point",
    "coordinates": [
      8.405393,
      49.008940
    ]
  }
}

###

### Get Square Centroid
GET http://localhost:8000/square/1/centroid

###

### Validate if the given point is inside square
GET http://localhost:8000/square/1/contain_point
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "point": {
    "type": "Point",
    "coordinates": [
      8.404335,
      49.009257
    ]
  }
}

###

### Delete square by id
DELETE http://localhost:8000/square/16

